item.title: Help with my Mod\Admin Teleport
item.dc:creator: @lool121 lool121
item.description:
@lool121 wrote:

I don’t know anything about delta but…

case 2472: //Staff portal if(playerRights >= 1 && (absX == 2990 && absY == 3379)) { toX = 2523; toY = 4649; sM("To the land of admins."); } else if(playerRights <= 1 && (absX == 2990 && absY == 3379)) { sM("You cannot use this teleport you are not mod or admin"); } break;

Doesn’t works?
Find this:

case 132: int objectX = inStream.readSignedWordBigEndianA();

If u can’t find this, i cannot help u further.
If u do found this, i’l help u further.

If u found the code at Case 132, u see something like this:

case 132: int objectX = inStream.readSignedWordBigEndianA(); int objectID = inStream.readUnsignedWord(); int objectY = inStream.readUnsignedWordA(); int face = 0; int face2 = 0; int GateID = 1;
Add this UNDER the case 132:

if(objectID == 2472)//staff portal { if(playerRights >=1){ toX = 2523; toY = 4649; sM("To the land of admins."); } else if(playerRights <=1){ sM("You cannot use this teleport you are not mod or admin"); } }
I hope it helpt, and else u need to find further.

- Lool121.
